    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Advanced computer labs in CSE department are very fascinating for true learner.",
          "name": "Bhagyashree Chitruk",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "i like the bus facility they provides bus to nearly all cities in kolhapur district",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "i persnolly like the locality of collage which is in center of the city",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Average Quality of Hostel,Big Library is there",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Very good faculty, supportive placement,",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "good and natural environment, also its not far away from city like other colleges.",
          "name": "Navanath bhosle",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "student section is there whenever you need any help. also you'll get best PCs .",
          "name": "Navanath bhosle",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "college campus because of a royal palace called RAJWADA its a palace of king narayan ghorpade and its DKTE now.",
          "name": "Navanath bhosle",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Great opportunities of working in textile field is given with 1 month internship program in 3rd year and final year which helps the student to understand the need of the industry and also helps understanding what actually the job they need to do",
          "name": "Nishit Kulkarni",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "There are many facilities like idea lab and other testing labs are available which helps students in there project related and research related work",
          "name": "Nishit Kulkarni",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "i have seen that some student misbehave with teachers and disturb other student also.",
          "name": "Vishwajit Balwan",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "There is no facility for students who cannot pay fees and are in Open category. There is assistance for students having Caste.",
          "name": "Abhishek Biyani",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The common room are not well maintained. Insufficieant supply of water",
          "name": "Bhagyashree Chitruk",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The management is little bit strict for discipline",
          "name": "Rushikesh Giri",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "the campus is to small and conjusted you can easily see back gate from entrence of collage",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Hostel should be more clean and good and decent",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Criteria of attendance is 75 persent is not good thing",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "overall a decent campus. but if you dont have an id card they wont allow you to enter in college",
          "name": "Navanath bhosle",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "campus is good but its smaller than other colleges",
          "name": "Navanath bhosle",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen facilities for breakfast, lunch, dinner are not that good",
          "name": "Nishit Kulkarni",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        }
      ]
